-- Old Mutual Aiming to IPO Its U.S. Asset Management Business by Mid-2011
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-08-06T06:53:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/old-mutual-aiming-to-ipo-its-u-s-asset-management-business-by-mid-2011.html

          
          
             Old Mutual Plc is aiming to sell
shares in its U.S. asset management unit by mid-2011, Chief
Executive Officer Julian Roberts said on a conference call from
London with reporters today.  
          
          


  


        